  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下基础设施层的交互关系。核心是从Infra_EtcdCluster出发，它作为配置中心，会驱动多个下游组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Infra_EtcdCluster是起点。那它首先要创建什么？是计算节点还是网络组件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "它会创建Infra_WorkerNode，也就是实际的工作节点。同时它还要启动Infra_IngressController来处理入口流量。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以Infra_EtcdCluster有两条出边：Creates指向Infra_WorkerNode，Starts指向Infra_IngressController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，而且Infra_EtcdCluster还需要向另一个Infra_WorkerNode实例报告状态，这里我们标记为Reports关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Reports和Creates都指向Infra_WorkerNode，但这是两个不同的实例还是同一个？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是不同的实例。Creates是初始化第一个工作节点，Reports是向另一个运行中的节点上报心跳或状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Reports关系。那负载均衡这块呢？Infra_EtcdCluster和Infra_LoadBalancer有交互吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有的，Infra_EtcdCluster会Contributes配置给Infra_LoadBalancer，同时也会Comments on它，也就是下发配置变更注释。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Contributes和Comments on都指向Infra_LoadBalancer。那Infra_WorkerNode和Infra_LoadBalancer之间呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Infra_WorkerNode会Receives来自Infra_LoadBalancer的流量，同样Infra_IngressController也会Receives。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
