    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里OtherUser其实是另一个Infra_IngressController实例，表示主从架构下的跟随关系。Follows描述的是配置同步行为。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，Follows指向另一个Infra_IngressController实例。那Badges和Rep是什么概念？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这是元数据层的概念。Infra_EtcdCluster Earns Badges，也就是从Infra_WorkerNode获取健康徽章标记；同时Gains Rep，从Infra_LoadBalancer获得声誉评分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Earns和Gains关系。现在来看各组件的状态属性，Infra_WorkerNode有什么特殊状态？",
